{"tid":143633,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中學老師：要勤力抄筆記","createTime":"2017-03-04T18:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-06T16:25:59.000Z","uid":36383,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b7319f4a5070fddeb56f6f885e4820d460fc9a2b","tid":143633,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T18:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 浪費體力，書都有嘅野點解要抄？要抄要寫都係書冇嘅或者整 summary 啦！<br />\n<br />\n啲教畜根本唔知咩係筆記，唔怪得要做老師。"},{"pid":"2799b8649ea4789a398429bfa3a9cea9dc6910ff","tid":143633,"uid":66527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T20:20:43.000Z","msg":"呢個問題我中學雞個陣都諗左好多 班on9老師成日話抄得愈多筆記=成績好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母, 抄得咁多把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抄就緊係抄重點 但重點又通常點洗抄咁多notes呢???<br />\n班垃圾學生係堂上面係又抄唔係又抄係到扮撚哂野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抄完唔溫咪又係無撚用<br />\n抄得多無用(已經識or書上有)既筆記仲會浪費自己溫習時間"},{"pid":"c771d9116b30f2c88e99abfc77941bb112de8e34","tid":143633,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T20:21:34.000Z","msg":"最撚on9就係話抄得愈多筆記=好學生<br />\n唔抄-&gt;個學生唔撚讀架啦"},{"pid":"b8d55617d42ac2e4124825ac7c865d3d9c451876","tid":143633,"uid":69779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T20:21:46.000Z","msg":"諗起張五常講過抄notes冇用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd98463b38204ee51ff097f6365050732123f2dc","tid":143633,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T20:25:41.000Z","msg":"如果係理科<br />\n明白左係會學得快好多<br />\n只抄一堆唔明既筆記<br />\n根本係一堆冇意義的符號<br />\n好快會唔記得"},{"pid":"f6b53fe6ab1313256dc05cb00bd06f9818b0c043","tid":143633,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:16:23.000Z","msg":"抄筆記浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n操下pp好過"},{"pid":"274bc50a5a37169c94237779cce676854499c4df","tid":143633,"uid":79373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:21:29.000Z","msg":"個筆記好亂 上網dl打PPT好過"},{"pid":"797c3a02cea59aea8bbcfab070be89999f9b473d","tid":143633,"uid":17322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:49:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43a6cd1311b665c016d3ce871b4e51f089b12f14","tid":143633,"uid":17322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:49:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c719f13b68bbfffa5c563591590db44064057de","tid":143633,"uid":72301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T03:53:50.000Z","msg":"照抄一定冇用，自己睇完曬書消化曬再整notes就好有用，抄一次好過睇書睇四五個鐘<br />\n<br />\n利申：本身自己極難專注溫書，但有支筆有張紙係手即刻有心機溫書好多"},{"pid":"ad45c16d41b013290d02907d2dca2e388c6559fe","tid":143633,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照抄一定冇用，自己睇完曬書消化曬再整notes就好有用，抄一次好過睇書睇四五個鐘<br />\n<br />\n利申：本身自己極難專注溫書，但有支筆有張紙係手即刻有心機溫書好多</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一路睇一路用支筆整理返個故仔 係有效率d"},{"pid":"7c33f1ecb6a83c4b92612606764689b3a7608b66","tid":143633,"uid":54132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:06:46.000Z","msg":"連大學班19有時都中意學生抄"},{"pid":"df4313366ffd5cd5ae2a072b31240d987c00d8ea","tid":143633,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:08:54.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ab523401e5899b13290ead38ed133f07265cf050","tid":143633,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:16:29.000Z","msg":"1. 要明<br />\n2. 要記<br />\n<br />\n良好筆記，有助你回憶返個邏輯同思路<br />\n抄寫過亦更容易記熟"},{"pid":"255aa38ac86b7fc60df2ecf95c23919282d5ac8e","tid":143633,"uid":44772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T04:24:17.000Z","msg":"中學miss逼人抄佢上堂講過嘅野 仲話要收返啲筆記嚟睇 好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00f63d5b50063d80a2f68877e56d64da4b75c31e","tid":143633,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T06:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學miss逼人抄佢上堂講過嘅野 仲話要收返啲筆記嚟睇 好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時真係想屌佢老母"},{"pid":"a0485d3a87e7d79fc3c4110fa62c57cf8afd873b","tid":143633,"uid":19141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T06:59:51.000Z","msg":"我剩係會炒老師d題外話<br />\n例如小學果陣常識老師唔知做乜講整腸仔<br />\n話係成隻豬放入攪肉機度<br />\nD豬驚就會瀬屎尿<br />\n所以食腸仔係會食埋豬屎尿<br />\n（搞到個成個小學生涯唔敢食腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n或者中學讀pure maths果陣老師講到個e好撚神奇<br />\n乜野股票點解市場變化萬千<br />\n幾千萬個人同時交易都可以咁準都係同個e有關<br />\n再唔係補chem個kkwong講條乜野iq150先解到既問題<br />\n一枝針隨機放落地<br />\n中間通過間隔同枝針一樣長既線<br />\n枝針撞到線既機率係幾多<br />\n唔知點解對依類野特別有興趣想抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7758d5504d2dd162bc22be75ee816e598118223","tid":143633,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抄筆記好有用喎<br />\n我數學同物理會抄<br />\n唔抄既話鬼識做啲數呀</blockquote><br />\nmath靠抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549ea51c2ea2aca2c7b96a038e79aeea5b133253","tid":143633,"uid":14675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:31:22.000Z","msg":"我抄筆記係為咗唔俾自己瞓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溫習溫人地嗰本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5499adbe09e92ef5af0054a74547acd1ce767d0","tid":143633,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:48:16.000Z","msg":"中學有個geog老師要人抄筆記，要交既，佢叫學生要精簡<br />\n<br />\n但要高分，係要抄哂成本書連圖都要用彩色畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5050609c2275c423af28ea1c1405b1164a66bea7","tid":143633,"uid":1044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:33:17.000Z","msg":"點樣寫一份好嘅筆記係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抄返啲內容入去個啲根本唔叫寫筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申仲學緊點樣去寫入好嘅筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3bf9b2435bbc3ffb303f828c800567bc3a9799a","tid":143633,"uid":72785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:36:32.000Z","msg":"從來無寫筆記習慣<br />\n只要上堂專心抄番重點出黎溫番就夠<br />\n成日都覺得寫筆記好浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a4590bc5997763d8ac53ea5c586329dafa03fa","tid":143633,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我剩係會炒老師d題外話<br />\n例如小學果陣常識老師唔知做乜講整腸仔<br />\n話係成隻豬放入攪肉機度<br />\nD豬驚就會瀬屎尿<br />\n所以食腸仔係會食埋豬屎尿<br />\n（搞到個成個小學生涯唔敢食腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n或者中學讀pure maths果陣老師講到個e好撚神奇<br />\n乜野股票點解市場變化萬千<br />\n幾千萬個人同時交易都可以咁準都係同個e有關<br />\n再唔係補chem個kkwong講條乜野iq150先解到既問題<br />\n一枝針隨機放落地<br />\n中間通過間隔同枝針一樣長既線<br />\n枝針撞到線既機率係幾多<br />\n唔知點解對依類野特別有興趣想抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔會成隻豬放啦<br />\n<br />\n唔同部位唔同價錢成本<br />\n<br />\n係放D市場少人用既肉,所以都唔會有屎尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(中國工廠就唔知"},{"pid":"6a246c70f692d662f1daa0ce2ce73b00e6d13240","tid":143633,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從來無寫筆記習慣<br />\n只要上堂專心抄番重點出黎溫番就夠<br />\n成日都覺得寫筆記好浪費時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專心聽老師up仲好啦"},{"pid":"ae3a0be5f629c6d21fdd6ca51879acf8eb215daa","tid":143633,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"抄筆記其實好有用<br />\n例如啲化學科，可以將一編介紹減到幾個公式<br />\n物理啲證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c39305a8ad2e459019b94a93f40190f3e75b2d","tid":143633,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:22:20.000Z","msg":"我份筆記係邏輯圖 好多線同箭咀<br />\n知道個邏輯先知點樣問問題"},{"pid":"0b68f6ef0a91682ab2a03e749395c797034f530e","tid":143633,"uid":29438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:23:45.000Z","msg":"啲老師成日叫我地抄<br />\n次次都拎d廢紙/是但係書到抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抄完唔知丟去邊"},{"pid":"bb52fff7ebc420f6c67eee04975b821fb54f4317","tid":143633,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:29:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣寫一份好嘅筆記係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抄返啲內容入去個啲根本唔叫寫筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申仲學緊點樣去寫入好嘅筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇整理過D叫罰抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3d97041063829b5d68ab384e40eb466fed2df3","tid":143633,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:32:41.000Z","msg":"讀到大學就知notes無用<br />\ntextbook已經係精華黎<br />\n無野可以再濃縮"},{"pid":"479e0d18ebf050c6fc073075d177e6065159f97b","tid":143633,"uid":62373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:37:00.000Z","msg":"舊時教得書都係讀書唔叻果班<br />\n當然真心教之外<br />\n<br />\n上唔琴大學先會去讀教協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce3718e7972717d7c5eebf2517ec301350a6efb","tid":143633,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:39:02.000Z","msg":"整notes係叫你用自己既文字同邏輯將學過既野演繹返出黎<br />\n相等於叫你唔好跟書讀，可以用自己語言教人一次咁<br />\n你就當係抄本書搬字過紙叫抄左notes <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9cd7f5ab8241e9fe8852aea2bed680e708cef7","tid":143633,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:39:14.000Z","msg":"當溫書嘅其實<br />\n因為就咁叫你聽書，未必知你係咪真係聽緊<br />\n抄一次重點可以逼你立下咁"},{"pid":"32dcb0790fb2e9c9e67c8716b5086ac02fa9db5c","tid":143633,"uid":78761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:42:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊時教得書都係讀書唔叻果班<br />\n當然真心教之外<br />\n<br />\n上唔琴大學先會去讀教協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打冇報過jupas？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6319208b0e32e155f3b391ce19149271a8f3f21","tid":143633,"uid":21871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:45:36.000Z","msg":"抄完會入腦d<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"589e94252b0be57c2eb935e90c74e56e89fddfd7","tid":143633,"uid":67823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:46:43.000Z","msg":"諗起以前中學有個同學<br />\n乜鳩都抄 書 pp 自己補習notes 借人補習notes<br />\n份筆記幾乎厚撚過本恐龍書<br />\n<br />\n雖然好似隻牛咁勤力 不過依然單位數<br />\n根本就溫唔哂記唔哂咁撚多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a337828deaac58fbc064f5cf3e274cef271769","tid":143633,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>舊時教得書都係讀書唔叻果班<br />\n當然真心教之外<br />\n<br />\n上唔琴大學先會去讀教協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打冇報過jupas？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去教協做超市收銀就有佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cac16342318b6eaedb19e79c74d534e5e9e98b1","tid":143633,"uid":51989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:00:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4b6321d9852bf4f95e5aa4b9bb916e2bfd0ccc8","tid":143633,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:05:50.000Z","msg":"中史抄真係好啲<br />\n抄咗易熟啲"},{"pid":"9008cef64896891ef021d5589af14e3d2d682a71","tid":143633,"uid":83807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:08:54.000Z","msg":"做一份pastpaper入哂腦啦<br />\n戇鳩仔先會溫筆記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739eac34f131cb881812326903a34b639a9b41e2","tid":143633,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個問題我中學雞個陣都諗左好多 班on9老師成日話抄得愈多筆記=成績好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母, 抄得咁多把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抄就緊係抄重點 但重點又通常點洗抄咁多notes呢???<br />\n班垃圾學生係堂上面係又抄唔係又抄係到扮撚哂野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抄完唔溫咪又係無撚用<br />\n抄得多無用(已經識or書上有)既筆記仲會浪費自己溫習時間</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔抄 notes 個 sem 比抄notes 考得好啲"},{"pid":"c245f28a7d550bb5bcfb3fda2060e0e2a0f6ea95","tid":143633,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起張五常講過抄notes冇用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 張六常繼承張五常學說"},{"pid":"caf6aefe51267860e00f6d26a74cab1a090d8c14","tid":143633,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:11:03.000Z","msg":"由細到大抄書都冇用腦<br />\n俾我抄一億次都係唔會記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977192ecaf3328bf5207ee9f0a9707192d00e831","tid":143633,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抄筆記好有用喎<br />\n我數學同物理會抄<br />\n唔抄既話鬼識做啲數呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Multivariable cal 一隻字都冇寫過"},{"pid":"5b8e8de2fed326280be0a8938dcad6b6b7ba4e78","tid":143633,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照抄一定冇用，自己睇完曬書消化曬再整notes就好有用，抄一次好過睇書睇四五個鐘<br />\n<br />\n利申：本身自己極難專注溫書，但有支筆有張紙係手即刻有心機溫書好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsummary 真係有用，省時間"},{"pid":"b56c227987c44f27a1dc57e1e4f6320f05e53cf5","tid":143633,"uid":1914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:11:52.000Z","msg":"用緊cornell method，暫時唔錯"},{"pid":"7b01120e63d878901ba4e3f8c2860a22ed624347","tid":143633,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:13:25.000Z","msg":"D野係抄過先記到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3e51c08940315e14aec339bb5b3ded5268d44b","tid":143633,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:15:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我份筆記係邏輯圖 好多線同箭咀<br />\n知道個邏輯先知點樣問問題</blockquote><br />\n好中意呢啲筆記，好清晰"},{"pid":"637a91f9d63d915c365aab843141043559669ad9","tid":143633,"uid":17888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:21:18.000Z","msg":"抄左一次其實等於啲野你個腦run 左一次，當然啲人on99 乜都照抄另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bd9febff5b47d60c3461469ce481256af629ce","tid":143633,"uid":23423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:31:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>舊時教得書都係讀書唔叻果班<br />\n當然真心教之外<br />\n<br />\n上唔琴大學先會去讀教協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打冇報過jupas？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n四十年代個陣教書係讀師專就得<br />\n不過個班灰都化埋<br />\n依家最老個班係香港得兩間大學個陣嘅大學生啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f113f274477f6b955336534800dc2916f649c9b6","tid":143633,"uid":28472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>舊時教得書都係讀書唔叻果班<br />\n當然真心教之外<br />\n<br />\n上唔琴大學先會去讀教協<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實宜家教書果班都多數係唔叻架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}